Invocation Name: maybe bot
des: Not sure of an answer but don't want to be the one to say it? Finally, a bot for you! From the maker of No Bot and Yes Bot comes Maybe Bot! Will I be getting out of bed today? Are great things likely in my future? You shouldn't know for sure the answer to any of these, and neither does Maybe Bot!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
